author: elecharny
msg: Replaced the user explicit message by a generic one to defeat a potential exploit. A malevolent user won't know if the bind failed because the password is incorrect or because the principalDN is non existent.

author: sisbell
msg: Replaced the old profile injector code with new profile code. Merged project builders.

author: dkulp
msg: [CXF-2034] Add lifecycle listener to make sure the listeners are shutdown
If the user specifies a CorrelationID and the destination cannot handle that, bring up a new temporary queue to handle it to avoid a "hang".
